The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which makes it relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of social media data, which could potentially fall under cs.SD (Social and Information Networks) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
